snippet.title: SPACE SPROUTS | Official Release Window Trailer
snippet.description:
Space Sprouts is coming out early 2025! Check out the new demo! Wishlist now on Steam! ✨🌱

What is Space Sprouts about?
🌱 A challenging space adventure with cozy vibes!
✨ Explore your spaceship in 10-minute loops!

🚀 REVEAL the MYSTERIES of your spaceship
🧪 BEND the rules of PHYSICS
🔧 EXPERIMENT with strange gadgets and items
🌟 REPEAT and IMPROVE

Play our new demo on Steam and check our socials for insights into the development!

#indiegames #spacegame #cozygames
